      def group_salutation(old_salutation):
       if old_salutation == 'Mr':
          return('Mr')
       else:
          if old_salutation == 'Mrs':
             return('Mrs')
          else:
             if old_salutation == 'Master':
                return('Master')
             else: 
                if old_salutation == 'Miss':
                   return('Miss')
                else:
                   return('Others')
